                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3bn9xv3w/manifest/annotation/p2",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>The lot we bought from <persName>Mr Jacobs</persName> for the\n                                        Synagogue was sold<lb/> by the same far below its real\n                                        value, in consideration of its<lb/> purpose, it has a front\n                                        of 70 feet (by 75 in depth) its location is<lb/> central and\n                                        it is our plan to erect a plain but handsome building,<lb/>\n                                        the cost of which shall not exceed $6000 including fixtures,\n                                        and<lb/> it shall at the same time have school Rooms for\n                                        religious instruction.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Any contribution, small as the amount may be, will\n                                        therefore be<lb/> thankfully received and be of great\n                                        benefit towards a speedy<lb/> accomplishment of these\n                                        designs.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I do not think of anything else that might be of\n                                        interest<lb/> for you, except that some of our Israelites,\n                                        though foremost<lb/> in contributing for the relief of the\n                                        suffering emigrants<lb/> desained[?] as and about\n                                                  <placeName>Cairo</placeName> by [?]ce, have made\n                                        among themselves<lb/> besides this an extra collection and\n                                        handed $100.00 as<lb/> a present of a Jewish society for the\n                                        same purpose to the<lb/> mayor of this city.</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With feelings of confidence in your zeal that\n                                        will<lb/> leave this call go lost, and with the assurance\n                                        of<lb/> my perfect esteem and affection</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Yours</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Isidor Bush</persName>\n                              </p>\n                    </body>\n          </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3bn9xv3w/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
